OL,3,CGinsters owner fined #1.28m after man
OL,4,Ccrushed to death by lorry at bakery
OL,6,FThe owner of Cornish-pasty makers
OL,7,FGinsters has been fined #1.28 million
OL,8,Fafter an employee was killed by one of
OL,9,Fits lorries delivering supplies to a
OL,10,Fbakery.
OL,12,FPaul Clarke died on 2 December 2021
OL,13,Fafter being crushed by the vehicle as
OL,14,Fit reversed into a loading bay at The
OL,15,FCornwall Bakery in Callington.
OL,17,FThe 40-year-old had recently joined
OL,18,Fthe bakery as an intake operator and
OL,19,Fhad been moving strip curtains in the
OL,20,Floading bay when he was hit by the
OL,21,Florry.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
