OL,6,FHe was taken to Derriford Hospital
OL,7,Fwhere he later died.
OL,9,FMr Clarke's mother described him as a
OL,10,F"family man" and said she has been
OL,11,Fleft so devastated she no longer
OL,12,Fcelebrates Christmas as it is too
OL,13,Fclose to the anniversary of her son's
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,FThe pastry-makers are operated by
OL,17,FSamworth Brothers and a Health and
OL,18,FSafety Executive (HSE) investigation
OL,19,Ffound it had not assessed the risks
OL,20,Fassociated with the temporarily
OL,21,Finstalled strip curtains.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
