OL,6,FIt also found there was no safe system
OL,7,Fof work to move them out of the way
OL,8,Fwhen the lorries reversed into the
OL,9,Floading bay.
OL,11,FThe strip curtains had been installed
OL,12,Fin place of a faulty roller door.
OL,14,FThe HSE investigation found the site
OL,15,Fstaff had not been provided with
OL,16,Ftraining or instructions to move the
OL,17,Fcurtains and had devised their own
OL,18,Fmethods, which included standing in
OL,19,Fthe yard behind reversing vehicles.
