OL,6,FMr Clarke was new to the role and was
OL,7,Fworking his first lone shift and
OL,8,Fmanagement failings had not picked up
OL,9,Fthe additional risks associated with
OL,10,Fthis task.
OL,12,FSamworth Brothers Limited, of Samworth
OL,13,FWay, Melton Mowbray, Leicestershire,
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to breaching Section
OL,15,F2(1) of the Health and Safety at Work
OL,16,Fetc. Act 1974.
OL,18,FThe company was fined #1.28million and
OL,19,Fordered to pay #24,106 in costs at
OL,20,FPlymouth Magistrates' Court on 7
OL,21,FNovember.
