OL,6,FPaul's mother Bernice said in a
OL,7,Fstatement: "Paul was a family man and
OL,8,Floved big family holidays, which will
OL,9,Fnever be the same without him.
OL,11,F"I have not been on a family holiday
OL,12,Fsince I feel so much guilt towards
OL,13,FPaul, we don't celebrate Christmas as
OL,14,Fthe date is too close and it is just
OL,15,Fnot the same.
OL,17,F"Paul and I had a very special
OL,18,Frelationship between a mother and a
OL,19,Fson.
