OL,6,F"We were always talking and catching
OL,7,Fup. I would call him every weekend and
OL,8,Fsee what he was doing.
OL,10,F"He would always come out with us on a
OL,11,Fbike ride or a walk. We all miss Paul
OL,12,Fvery much every day, our lives will
OL,13,Fnever be the same without Paul."
OL,15,FHSE inspector Aimie Baker said:
OL,16,F"Bernice's words make clear the impact
OL,17,Fthe passing of Paul has had and our
OL,18,Fthoughts remain with her and her
OL,19,Ffamily.
