OL,6,F"Workplace transport incidents
OL,7,Finvolving pedestrians are a major
OL,8,Fcause of fatal injuries in the
OL,9,Fworkplace with 25 such recorded
OL,10,Ffatalities in 2023/24.
OL,12,F"Employers should plan their workplace
OL,13,Fto reduce contact between pedestrians
OL,14,Fand vehicles.
OL,16,F"Their risk assessment should consider
OL,17,Fworkplace transport activities,
OL,18,Fincluding loading and unloading, and
OL,19,Fensure that pedestrians are safe from
OL,20,Fthe risks associated with vehicle
OL,21,Fmovements where they interact.
