OL,6,FIn a statement, Samworth Brothers
OL,7,Fsaid: "We were deeply shocked and
OL,8,Fsaddened by the vehicle-related
OL,9,Faccident at our Cornwall Bakery site
OL,10,Fin December 2021 that resulted in the
OL,11,Fdeath of Paul Clarke.
OL,13,F"The Cornwall Bakery is a strong
OL,14,Fcommunity of friends and colleagues.
OL,15,FPaul was such a positive influence on
OL,16,Feveryone that knew him and a much-
OL,17,Floved and respected member of our team.
OL,19,F"Health and safety is our highest
OL,20,Fpriority and it is vital to learn from
OL,21,Fsuch events.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
